      <title>阿里巴巴创始人马云走出阴影，发表长篇内部文章</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-founder-jack-ma-steps-out-shadows-with-long-internal-post-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴联合创始人马云罕见地给员工写了一份长篇备忘录，表达了对这家互联网巨头重组工作的支持，这表明他在过去几年远离聚光灯后可能愿意扮演更积极的角色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-founder-jack-ma-steps-out-shadows-with-long-internal-post-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:03:17 GMT</pubDate>
